title: Act3
---
The basement door shuts behind me.
A heavy lock engages.
Rows of servers echo across the basement
BigBoss: You're one last step.
BigBoss: Go find the files
===

title: Act3_End
---
I press the power button
...
Nothing.
Then-
The system boots instantly.
WELCOME BACK.
The text vanishes.
BigBoss: That was immediate.
BigBoss: Systems like this don't just—
The screen floods a lot of lights.
Access granted.
BigBoss: You didn't authenticate?
Data begins to scroll.
BigBoss: This isn't storage.
BigBoss: It's running something. 
BigBoss: I've heard of places like this…
BigBoss: Black sites disguised as corporate offices.
BigBoss: Not for storing data—
BigBoss: For testing behavior.
A file opens.
Then another.
Then hundreds.
LIQUID MONGOOSE.
BigBoss: …
BigBoss: That's you.
Designation: LIQUID MONGOOSE SERIES. 
Status: Active / Deployed.  
Iteration Count: Redacted.
BigBoss: “Series”…?
More data appears.
Deployment logs.
Failure states.
Termination records.
BigBoss: These aren't reports.
BigBoss: They are iterations.
BigBoss: The Black Company doesn't recruit talent.
BigBoss: They refine it.
BigBoss: Over and over again… until it stops failing.
BigBoss: Mongoose…
BigBoss: Some of these timestamps—
BigBoss: They are in the future.
A live feed appears.
This room.
Me—standing at the terminal.
BigBoss: …
BigBoss: It was waiting for you.
    ->Me: Waiting?
BigBoss: You didn't access the system.
BigBoss: You activated it.
BigBoss: This place isn't storing you.
BigBoss: It's producing you.
BigBoss: Those workers upstairs—
BigBoss: Did they react to you at all?
…
BigBoss: We need to move.
BigBoss: Now.
BigBoss: Take whatever data you can.
BigBoss: And listen carefully—
BigBoss: If this system can replace you…
BigBoss: no one will know the difference.
A deep brief pause.
BigBoss: Mongoose…
BigBoss: If you're seeing this…
BigBoss: Then you're not the first one to make it this far.
    -> Leave the server room.
        <<winScreen>>
===

